      "writtenOn": "2026-06-12T21:08:46Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think this is true: for a message with multiple editions, the code currently works only if `updateMessageBodyOverwrite` is called in the correct order (older editions before newer ones). Even if this is the case for the translation plugin, it\u0027s probably better not to assume it.",
      "parentUuid": "483568a8_6c791956",
      "revId": "055abc280f1f60d21f55d5b30420814ce746552b",
